      "writtenOn": "2018-07-28T06:21:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "OK, dst is the image rectangle, not the frame rectangle. But is onIncrementalDecode (and onGetPixels) supposed to touch the pixels of dst that are outside the frame-rect but inside the image-rect? See also the \"clear the dst image to transparent black\" in my newer patch set.",
